Hypo’s Bad Bank May Have Billion-Euro Loss, Der Spiegel Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-09T12:47:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/hypo-s-bad-bank-may-have-billion-euro-loss-der-spiegel-says.html
Hypo Real Estate Holding AG’s FMS
Wertmanagement bad bank is likely to have a billion-euro loss
when it reports earnings,  Der Spiegel  said.  Christian Bluhm, head of FMS Wertmanagement, made the
comment to  Germany ’s parliamentary financial committee
yesterday, the magazine reported.  Der Spiegel  did not specify
the amount of the loss.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
